column2: Table 5#9#4B# Price Indexes for Gross Government Fixed Investmen
1. Consists of general government and government enterprise expenditures for fixed assets.
2. Structures, software, and research and development include compensation of government employees engaged
in new own-account investment and related expenditures for goods and services.
3. Consists of Department of Defense new structures, except family housing.
4. Consists of lodging, religious, communication, sewage and waste disposal, water supply structures,
5. Consists of lodging, communication, and manufacturing.
